=================
setuptools-github
=================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/click-plus.svg
   :target: https://pypi.org/project/click-plus
   :alt: PyPI version

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/click-plus.svg
